183.description: Supports melee attack skills, making them repeat twice when used, targeting a random enemy each time. Cannot support Vaal skills, totem skills, channelling skills, or triggered skills.

184.description: Supports spell skills, making them repeat when cast. Cannot support Vaal skills, totem skills, channelling skills, triggered skills, or skills which reserve mana.

190.description: Must support both a skill that hits enemies, and a curse skill to work. The curse will be applied when enemies are hit by the other skill. Cannot support totems, traps, or mines. Minions cannot apply curses this way.

193.description: Must support both an attack skill and a spell skill to work. The attack skill will trigger a spell when it critically strikes an enemy. Cannot support totems, traps, or mines. Vaal skills and skills that reserve mana cannot be triggered.

194.description: Must support both a melee attack skill and a spell skill to work. The attack skill will trigger a spell when it kills an enemy.  Cannot support totems, traps, or mines. Vaal skills and skills that reserve mana cannot be triggered.

195.description: Supports traps skills, making them throw extra traps in a line.

196.description: Supports any skill gem. Once this gem reaches level 2 or above, will raise the level of supported gems. Cannot support skills that don't come from gems.

206.description: Supports any skill that has a duration.

207.description: Each supported spell skill will be triggered when you die. Cannot support Totems, Traps, or Mines. Vaal skills and skills that reserve mana cannot be triggered.

208.description: Each supported spell skill will track damage you take, and be triggered when the total damage taken reaches a threshold. Cannot support totems, traps, or mines. Vaal skills and skills that reserve mana cannot be triggered.

209.description: Each supported spell skill will have a chance to be triggered when you are stunned. Cannot support Totems, Traps, or Mines. Vaal skills and skills that reserve mana cannot be triggered.

211.description: Supports any skill gem. Once this gem reaches level 2 or above, will raise the quality of supported gems. Cannot support skills that don't come from gems.

226.description: Supports any skill gem. Once this gem reaches level 2 or above, will apply a mana multiplier to supported gems. Cannot support skills that don't come from gems.

232.description: Supports any skill that hits enemies.

238.description: Supports aura skills that affect you and allies, increasing the aura's effect on allies, but preventing if from affecting you at all. Cannot support curse auras, or other auras that only affect enemies. Cannot support Totems.
